data.title: Jason Kidd and Jim - Image 2 from 7 Times Athletes Beefing Over Women Had Us Like Whoa
data.meta_description: Jason Kidd and Jim Jackson Involved With Toni Braxton - The Dallas Mavericks were building a nice young nucleus in the 1990s with the three Js — Jamal Mashburn, Jason Kidd (left) and Jim Jackson (right). According to legend, the latter two vied for the attention of R&B diva Toni Braxton, which eventually led to the Mavs' three stars being dismantled.(Photos from Left: Jonathan Daniel/Getty Images, Thaddaeus McAdams/FilmMagic) - Some of these stories were way out of bounds.
